```

#### Common Issues
- **Projects not updating:** Check for uncommitted files (M marker in VS Code Source Control) — commit before deploying
- **ESLint blocking build:** `package.json` build script should be `"build": "vite build"` not `"build": "npm run lint && vite build"`
- **Husky blocking commits:** Use `git commit --no-verify -m "message"`

#### deploy.sh
```bash
#!/bin/bash
echo "Adding all changes..."
git add .
echo "Enter commit message:"
read -r commit_message
git commit -m "$commit_message"
git push origin main
npm run deploy
echo "✅ Deployment complete! Check: https://summerjyl.github.io/Portfolio/"
```

